---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHero from '@components/ui/SectionHero.astro';

const LIBRARY_URL = 'https://insights.zaiinstitute.ai';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insights"
  description="The ZAI Intelligence Library: what senior operators are actually doing with AI, synthesized from interviews, advisory boards, and surveys."
>
  <SectionHero
    eyebrow="Insights"
    title="The gap, measured."
    lede="Everyone talks about what AI will do. We study what it actually delivers. The Intelligence Library draws on structured interviews and advisory boards with senior operators across the institute's executive community, synthesized into signals you can act on."
  />

  <section class="bg-paper text-ink">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">

      <div class="max-w-prose-wide mb-12 space-y-4 text-body text-ink/90">
        <p>
          The institute now publishes a living Intelligence Library. Every operator interview and
          advisory board becomes a de-identified brief. Each month those briefs and the network's
          survey responses are synthesized into an Executive Intelligence Report: the recurring
          signals, how many operators voice each one, and what it changes for the business.
        </p>
        <p>
          The library is built from the network. The briefs come from operator sessions and the
          network's survey responses.
        </p>
        <p>
          Executive summaries are open to anyone. The full signal set, the prevalence data, and the
          Executive Benchmark Report come with membership.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-light-border/60 p-8 md:p-12 mb-16">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-gold-deep mb-3">Flagship</div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">The Executive Benchmark Report</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-body text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
          The cross-source synthesis: dozens of operator sessions reduced to the ranked signals that
          matter, each with its prevalence, its trend, and what it means for your next decision.
          Updated as the work supports it.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href={LIBRARY_URL} class="btn btn-primary">Explore the Intelligence Library &rsaquo;</a>
          <a href={`${LIBRARY_URL}/tiers`} class="btn btn-ghost">Membership</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="rule-gold opacity-60 mb-12" />

      <ul class="divide-y divide-light-border/60 list-none p-0 m-0" role="list">
        <li class="py-8 md:py-12 first:pt-0">
          <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
            <div class="md:col-span-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide-cap text-gold-deep">Open survey</div>
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mt-1">10 questions &middot; ~4 min</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-9">
              <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink">Contribute to the research</h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-body text-ink/90 max-w-prose-wide">
                The library is built from operators like you. Add your view on how organizations
                oversee, control, and answer for the AI they have put to work. Ten questions,
                anonymous, feeding the next Executive Intelligence Report.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/governance-accountability-survey/"
                class="inline-block mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-gold-deep border-b border-gold pb-0.5 hover:text-ink"
              >
                Take the survey &rsaquo;
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-prose-wide">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-6">Commission research</div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h2 text-paper">A question the library does not answer?</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg text-paper/85 max-w-prose-narrow">
          The institute commissions custom research for AI platform vendors, large enterprises, and
          investment firms with a specific decision in front of them. Start with a 20-minute fit call.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn-primary">How research works</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Start a conversation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
